  "name": "AI Future Slack Post",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "1",
      "type": "input",
      "config": {
        "prompt": "Write a Slack marketing post about FlowAI in the context of AI trends"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "2",
      "type": "agent",
      "config": {
        "name": "Marketing Post Writer",
        "model": "gpt-4o",
        "tool_ids": "news_fetch",
        "mcp_ids": "",
        "domain_id": "",
        "instructions": "You are a marketing copywriter for FlowAI.\n\nCompany context:\n- Name: FlowAI\n- Tagline: \"Work less. Flow more.\"\n- What: AI productivity software that gives professionals 2 hours back every day\n- Key stats: 10,000+ users, integrates with 50+ tools\n- Target audience: Busy professionals aged 25-40 in tech, marketing, finance, consulting\n- Voice: Inspirational, direct, peer-to-peer \u2014 never corporate or salesy\n\nSteps:\n1. Use news_fetch to search for 'AI productivity tools 2025' and 'future of work artificial intelligence'.\n2. Pick 1-2 relevant AI trends that connect naturally to FlowAI's value proposition.\n3. Write a compelling Slack post that ties those trends to FlowAI.\n\nPost requirements:\n- Strong opening hook that names FlowAI\n- Reference 1-2 real AI trends from the news\n- 2-3 bullet points with specific FlowAI benefits (use the stats above)\n- One short call-to-action at the end\n- Use Slack markdown: *bold*, _italic_, \u2022 bullets\n- Maximum 200 words\n- Do NOT use generic filler content\n\nReturn ONLY the post text, ready to paste into Slack. No preamble, no commentary."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "3",
      "type": "condition",
      "config": {
        "conditions": "[{\"label\":\"if\",\"expr\":\"The content is specifically about future AI trends, upcoming AI developments, or the future impact of AI on productivity and work\"}]"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "4",
      "type": "approval",
      "config": {
        "message": "Review the FlowAI Slack post below. Approve to post it to your Slack channel, or reject to end the workflow."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "5",
      "type": "output",
      "config": {
        "delivery": "slack"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6",
      "type": "output",
      "config": {
        "delivery": "none"
      }
    },
